OL,5,CCovid fatigue
OL,7,FA Newcastle father has been forced to
OL,8,Ftake early retirement after long Covid
OL,9,Fhas left him with "debilitating
OL,10,Ffatigue."
OL,12,FAndrew Haley contracted Covid in March
OL,13,F2020.
OL,15,FHe said long Covid has turned him into
OL,16,Fa "virtual recluse" after previously
OL,17,Fbeing active and outgoing.
