OL,5,CCovid fatigue
OL,7,FIt comes as a report published today,
OL,8,Fthat explores Long Covid rates across
OL,9,FEngland, has shown the North East of
OL,10,FEngland has the second highest rates
OL,11,Fof people reporting long covid
OL,12,Fsymptoms in England.
OL,14,FAndrew Haley told our reporter Helen
OL,15,FFord that long Covid has turned him
OL,16,Finto a "recluse"
OL,18,FSixty Three year old Andrew Haley said
OL,19,Flong Covid forced him to give up a job
OL,20,Fhe enjoyed and take early retirement.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
