OL,7,FHe added: "It's been devastating.
OL,8,FThat's the word I can use, yeah,
OL,9,Fdevastating because it's like I am
OL,10,Fliving a different life now prior to
OL,11,Fthe life I lived pre-Covid.
OL,13,F"I don't socialise any more, I can't
OL,14,Fphysically do much actively, so I
OL,15,Fdon't go to the gym any more, I don't
OL,16,Fgo out and basically, I am housebound."
