OL,5,CCovid fatigue
OL,7,FThe report published today was put
OL,8,Ftogether by a group of health
OL,9,Facademics. It suggested that cases
OL,10,Flike Mr Haley's are far more prevalent
OL,11,Facross the north than elsewhere in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FExamining patient surveys carried out
OL,15,Fby GP practices, they found the
OL,16,Fhighest rates in the North West - with
OL,17,F5.5% of respondents reporting Long
OL,18,FCovid.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
