OL,5,CCovid fatigue
OL,7,FThe figure for the North East and
OL,8,FYorkshire stands slightly below, at
OL,9,F5.1% - with the England average at 4.4%
OL,11,FThe issue, according to the
OL,12,Fresearchers, isn't simply the number
OL,13,Fof people who are living with long
OL,14,FCovid - but the impact it is having on
OL,15,Ftheir lives, their families, wellbeing
OL,16,Fand employment prospects.
OL,18,FThe Government said it's committed to
OL,19,Fensuring everyone has access to the
OL,20,Fcare they need.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
