OL,7,FThe authors of today's report say long
OL,8,FCovid is adding to existing health
OL,9,Finequalities in our region - and are
OL,10,Fcalling for action.
OL,12,F"One of our recommendations from the
OL,13,Freport is a government consultation,
OL,14,Fboth with employers and with people
OL,15,Fliving with long Covid to kind of
OL,16,Fexplore ways that we could manage the
OL,17,Fcondition of long Covid but-so ways
OL,18,Fthat employers could potentially
OL,19,Fsupport their employees who are
OL,20,Fsuffering with post Covid condition."
