OL,7,FClaire Hastie runs a long Covid
OL,8,Fsupport group in County Durham and is
OL,9,Fpart of a global network of 65,000
OL,10,Fmembers.
OL,12,FShe said: "Theres a lot of people like
OL,13,Fmyself who are having to reduce hours
OL,14,For change their careers.
OL,16,F"A lot of people are losing their jobs
OL,17,Fand being fired because their
OL,18,Femployers are not prepared to make
OL,19,Faccommodations so it has a huge effect
OL,20,Fat individual level but also at
OL,21,Fsocietal level."
